    <item>
      <title>Experience</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/experience/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/experience/</guid>
      <description>&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 style=&#34;font-size:3.5rem; margin:0 0 -0.2em;&#34;&gt;Experience&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&gt;&#xA;My experience spans both industry and customer-facing environments, giving me a well-rounded foundation in technical problem-solving and interpersonal skills. During my placement year at Shell, I worked as a Data Scientist within the E-Mobility team, applying machine learning, data analysis, and software engineering to real-world energy and transport challenges. Prior to that, my time at Screwfix developed my communication, teamwork, and ability to perform under pressure - skills that continue to complement my technical work.&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;data-scientistshell&#34;&gt;Data Scientist &amp;mdash;&amp;ndash; Shell&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;082025---092026london&#34;&gt;08/2025 - 09/2026 &amp;mdash;&amp;ndash; London&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;My placement year as a Data Scientist within Shell&#39;s E-Mobility team in central London was an incredibly varied and rewarding experience, spanning data analysis, machine learning, and software engineering to support both research and development and strategic business decisions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
